* Carnage watched Cyber Claw fall and fly off into the horizon, she snarled 
and slammed her fist down onto Rage's nose.*

" COWARD!!!!!!!!"

*Suddenly Carnage felt herself fly into the air and she saw the ground 
rushing up towards her, the damned Tarbosaurs had thrown her and now she was 
experiencing the results!
Carnage twisted in mid-air and landed herd on her shoulder, she gasped as 
the air from her lung rushed out and left her breathless.
It was then that she looked up and saw how great the beast really was, it 
was black, grey and arms as long as a baby carriage hung in front of it. 
It's jaws were the size of a small car looked down at her.
Carnage gulped, what would it do now?*
